  including K-LISTK-EXTRAS .
  including K-LIST-EXTRAS .
  including K-MAP-EXTRAS .          --- operations on Maps
  including K-BAG-EXTRAS .          --- operations on Bags
  including K-SET-EXTRAS .          --- operations on Sets
  including K-LATEX .
endm


